00:11:19.607 --> 00:11:22.077
farshidene zakhn, yede za- oyf broyt

00:11:22.077 --> 00:11:24.067
bin ikh geshtanen in di reye

00:11:24.067 --> 00:11:26.483
vayl m'iz oyfgeshtanen zekse far togs

00:11:26.483 --> 00:11:28.457
un m'iz geshtanen oyf di reye

00:11:28.457 --> 00:11:31.984
un azoy arumet iz men tsugeganen tsu di, tsum gesheft

00:11:31.984 --> 00:11:34.783
hob ikh gekrign bald ge- krank gevorn oyf ⟨sharlekh⟩.

00:11:35.177 --> 00:11:38.124
un demolt sharlekh iz gevezn geferlekh.

00:11:38.687 --> 00:11:41.836
hob ikh shoyn gehat a QUARANTAINE fun zeks vokhn.

00:11:42.214 --> 00:11:44.722
mayne shvester hot men avekgeshikt keyn

00:11:44.830 --> 00:11:50.882
tsu di e- tsu di bobes, un ikh bin gekumen, geblibn zitsn in di shtub nor mit di goye.

00:11:51.073 --> 00:11:53.981
ales iz avek. di mame iz geshlofn in eyn shlof shtub

00:11:53.981 --> 00:11:59.691
di goye in di ts- in di kokh iz zi geshlofn, un ikh bin geshlofn aleyn in di shlof shtub, vayle di mame hot nisht gemegt tsu mir tsugeyn

00:11:59.713 --> 00:12:01.819
zol nisht aynshtekn yene mentshn

00:12:01.819 --> 00:12:04.094
un zi hot mikh nisht gevolt gebn in shpitol arayn.

00:12:05.215 --> 00:12:08.297
vi hot zikh bay aykh di tog teglekhe

00:12:08.691 --> 00:12:15.350
enderungen BEMERKBAR, vos, vos iz geven di ershte enderungen vos iz geven in ayer lebn?

00:12:15.357 --> 00:12:18.894
di ershte enderung iz gevezn vos mir hobn nisht gekent geyn in di shule.

00:12:19.002 --> 00:12:23.850
m'hot geshpilt stabil oyfn hoyf. mir hobn gehat a groysn hoyf, hobn mit geshpilt stabil in di hoyf

00:12:23.850 --> 00:12:27.348
un lang- un der tate iz geganen, hot tsugenumen a rebn

00:12:27.405 --> 00:12:30.075
un hot undz gelernt A.B.C. yidish

00:12:30.075 --> 00:12:33.175
davenen un, zoln mir hobn a bisele basheftikung.

00:12:33.175 --> 00:12:35.101
epes andersh hot er nisht gelernt.

00:12:35.101 --> 00:12:39.061
nor dos hot men gelernt, zol men kenen epes oyf shpeter, undz zoln mir nisht fargesn

00:12:39.061 --> 00:12:40.680
az ze'mir gevezn yidn.

00:12:40.821 --> 00:12:46.029
un m'hot nisht ge- ir hot nisht geklert fun avektsuloyfn tsi antloyfn demolts?

00:12:45.867 --> 00:12:51.415
neyn. m'hot nisht gehat vu tsu loyfn. der tate hot nisht gevolt, di mame hot nisht gevolt iberlozn di mishpokhe

00:12:51.415 --> 00:12:54.889
un m'hot nisht s- m'hot gekent, m'hot nisht gekent loyfn

00:12:55.384 --> 00:12:59.360
ir veyst fun mentshn vos zenen avekgeforn?

00:12:57.308 --> 00:13:03.034
dos iz gevezn shpeter vos zenen zey avekgeforn. frier z- iz gevezn veynik mentshn vos zenen avek

00:13:03.034 --> 00:13:08.064
f- shpeter az m'hot undz shoyn genumen in ge- in lager arayn, in geto, in lager

00:13:08.064 --> 00:13:12.224
hot men ongehoybn UNK avek. ABER vu iz men geforn? in di derfer arayn.

00:13:12.224 --> 00:13:17.521
m'iz geforn in di derfer, vayl m'hot gemeynt in derfer dort nisht pasirn gornisht, ober dos iz nisht vor.

00:13:17.521 --> 00:13:22.191
nisht lang iz dos gekumen alts in di derfer. JUSTE di zelbe. ze'mir takesh gevezn.

00:13:22.191 --> 00:13:23.581
zenen mir gevezn in Kroke.

00:13:23.581 --> 00:13:25.781
shpeter iz

00:13:25.781 --> 00:13:32.014
hot zikh ongehoybn vos hot men tsugenumen, hot geheysn opgebn dos gantse gold un dos gantse zilber

00:13:31.699 --> 00:13:33.988
ven iz dos geven UNK?

00:13:32.070 --> 00:13:32.958
un

00:13:33.167 --> 00:13:35.945
in, alts in geto nokh. alts in geto.

00:13:35.091 --> 00:13:39.422
ikh red nokh for dem geto, hot men, iz nisht geven keyn yidishe

00:13:38.938 --> 00:13:42.880
neyn, dos iz gevezn in insh- in, in Kroke, vu ikh hob gevoynt.

00:13:43.123 --> 00:13:45.187
hot men gemuzt ales opgebn

00:13:45.187 --> 00:13:50.477
m'hot UNK afile dos kleyntshike UNK radyo hot gedarft men opgebn, zol men nisht visn keyn nayes.

00:13:50.477 --> 00:13:54.730
ales hot men gemuzt opgebn. zenen zey gekumen in shtub arayn. zey hobn tsugenumen, m'hot gehat hengen

00:13:54.730 --> 00:13:58.130
vi haynt gedenk ikh az er hot ⟨tapet⟩ oyf di re- oyf di vant.

00:13:58.130 --> 00:13:59.720
hot er dos aropgenumen.

00:13:59.897 --> 00:14:04.467
ikh hob nisht farshtanen vos dos iz. dos hot gemuzt zayn a ekhte ⟨tapet⟩ vos hot UNK geganen

00:14:04.467 --> 00:14:06.711
aropnemen dem ⟨tapet⟩ der yeke.

00:14:06.711 --> 00:14:08.601
un zilber hot men tsugenumen

00:14:08.601 --> 00:14:16.448
un gold UNK. vos hot men gehat, hot men gemuzt gebn, az nisht hot men moyre gehat. der tate iz tsufelik nisht gevezn avade, nor di mame. der tate hot zikh gehaltn oyfn boydem.

00:14:16.448 --> 00:14:19.398
⟨BUT⟩ nokh alts nisht gevolt oy- oysshnaydn di bord.

00:14:19.398 --> 00:14:21.698
ABER shpeter, leyder, hot er gemuzt opshnaydn.

00:14:21.666 --> 00:14:26.250
un m'iz, hot gemuzt geyn mit a shtern oyf di gasn?

00:14:25.699 --> 00:14:30.345
yo. dos iz gevezn bald. azoy vi zenen zey arayngekumen di yekes, hobn mir shoyn gemuzt

00:14:30.345 --> 00:14:34.412
ontun a shtern yeder eyner fun ⟨dos⟩. undz ho'mir nisht ongetun, di kinder.

00:14:34.305 --> 00:14:38.636
un s'iz geven bagrenetst vu me meg geyn oder vos?

00:14:34.412 --> 00:14:35.480
UNK

00:14:37.765 --> 00:14:41.724
keyn TRAM hot men nisht gemegt forn. keyn tsug hot men nisht gemegt forn.

00:14:42.169 --> 00:14:47.237
⟨BUT⟩ m'hot nisht gemegt geyn tsu goyishe gesheftn aynkoyfn, nor alts tsvishn ⟨do⟩ tsvishn yidn.

00:14:47.237 --> 00:14:54.634
az s'hot men gevolt geyn oyf di lange gas, gevezn goyishe gesheftn azoy vi UNK ⟨WIELKY⟩ vos iz geven tshokolade vos hot men UNK dort gekoyft

00:14:54.943 --> 00:14:56.405
hot men nisht gemegt geyn.

00:14:56.867 --> 00:15:01.248
un vi iz geven di REAKTION fun di nisht yidishe bafelkerung, di

00:15:01.086 --> 00:15:02.767
oh, zey hobn ⟨es⟩ gehat hanoe.

00:15:03.297 --> 00:15:07.837
zey hobn g- hanoe. zey hobn gezogt az dos ⟨iz⟩ gevezn yidishe hayzer

00:15:07.837 --> 00:15:09.297
⟨un⟩ undzere gasn.

00:15:09.297 --> 00:15:11.177
yetst vet zayn undzere gas oy-

00:15:11.177 --> 00:15:14.366
gasn, un zeyer h- nisht keyn, nisht keyn yidn.

00:15:16.020 --> 00:15:19.470
yidishe h- hayzer ⟨un⟩ zeyere gasn zenen ⟨zey⟩ gevezn.

00:15:19.470 --> 00:15:22.270
un shpeter hobn zey gezogt az dos vet zayn undzere gasn

00:15:22.270 --> 00:15:24.396
undzere gasn, undzere hayzer.

00:15:24.396 --> 00:15:26.190
oh, zey hobn gehat hanoe mit dem.

00:15:26.719 --> 00:15:28.215
zey hobn gehat hanoe.

00:15:28.980 --> 00:15:33.277
un vos, vi hot zikh ongehoybn di shmue fun dem

00:15:33.351 --> 00:15:36.618
tsu geyn in a geto? gedenkt ir fun dem?

00:15:35.325 --> 00:15:41.515
yo. zey hobn gezogt az zey makhn dos a plats far undz, a spetsyeln PODGORZE, a spetsyel plats

00:15:41.515 --> 00:15:45.123
undz ⟨veln mir⟩ ale dort voynen, un fun dort veln mir geyn tsu di arbet.

00:15:45.282 --> 00:15:51.556
nor azoy az UNK ongehoybn, hot mayn tate hot UNK gevust UNK kleyne kinder, hot takesh nisht gevolt blaybn

00:15:51.556 --> 00:15:57.104
in Kroke, iz er geforn keyn SKAWINA. dos iz a dorf ⟨arayn⟩. mir ho'mir gehat dort mishpokhe.

00:15:57.212 --> 00:16:02.027
iz er geforn keyn dorf arayn, un m'hot gedungen dort a WOHNUNG, un m'hot dort ge- gelebt.

00:16:02.027 --> 00:16:04.125
ABER dos hot nisht lang gedoyert.

00:16:04.148 --> 00:16:08.937
bald zenen zey gekumen, hobn zey gezogt vider di ale dorfn kumen keyn Kroke vider tsurik

00:16:08.937 --> 00:16:10.793
keyn UNK keyn PODGORZE

00:16:10.793 --> 00:16:12.157
in geto arayn

00:16:12.180 --> 00:16:15.599
un mir ⟨hobn⟩ UNK ale bald tsurikgekumen in geto arayn.

00:16:15.370 --> 00:16:17.389
vu iz geven DET geto?

00:16:17.530 --> 00:16:19.397
di geto iz in PODGORZE

00:16:19.881 --> 00:16:21.160
dos iz

00:16:20.044 --> 00:16:21.711
oyf di JOZEFINSKI.

00:16:21.711 --> 00:16:23.901
iz gevez- gevezn di geto.

00:16:21.901 --> 00:16:23.781
dos iz geven

00:16:23.901 --> 00:16:26.331
dos iz geven d- a gantse

00:16:26.490 --> 00:16:30.815
vi me zogt a ⟨kleyne⟩ shtetele arum un arum, un ale yidn hobn dort gevoynt.

00:16:30.815 --> 00:16:32.562
es iz gevezn arum un arum

00:16:32.562 --> 00:16:33.740
drotn

00:16:34.118 --> 00:16:38.735
un zey hobn gemakht di kleyne hayzelekh. zey hobn oyfgepast UNK zoln mir undz nisht loyfn

00:16:38.860 --> 00:16:41.337
un di TRAM iz adurkhgeforn

00:16:41.337 --> 00:16:44.459
durkhn geto, azoy az hot men gekent zikh

00:16:44.459 --> 00:16:47.952
a bisl aroysganvenen, undz kinder perzenlekh

00:16:47.952 --> 00:16:50.092
hobn mir zikh gekent aroys⟨UNK⟩ vos

00:16:50.098 --> 00:16:54.108
vayl di TRAM iz geforn eyns oyf eyn zayt, un eyne ⟨ON⟩ di tsveyte zayt

00:16:54.108 --> 00:16:59.348
un tsvishn iz gevezn a groyse oyfmakhn, un do iz geshtanen a budke mit a yeke

00:16:59.363 --> 00:17:02.465
un undz ze'mir gegebn az er iz tsvishn dem adurkhgeforn

00:17:02.465 --> 00:17:04.582
hobn mir nokh gehat a bisele gelt

00:17:04.582 --> 00:17:10.802
iz men aroysgelofn oyfn mark, un me hot gekoyft a bisele broyt, a bisele mel, zol men kenen op- kartofl

00:17:10.802 --> 00:17:14.988
⟨vayl m'iz dokh⟩ gevezn zeyer ⟨opbatsimpert⟩ mit hundert tsvontsik gram broyt.

00:17:15.411 --> 00:17:20.957
vos iz pasirt mit ayere zakhn in, in ayer hoyz? hot ir gedarft zey VERLASSEN?

00:17:19.123 --> 00:17:24.736
demolts fun Kroke, yo, demolts fun Kroke vu undz ze'mir dort UNK gemuzt farlozn

00:17:24.912 --> 00:17:34.474
hot men alts gegebn eyn goye oyfn partey, az zi iz gevezn undz a neytorin, vos zi hot undz alts geneyt di kleyder, hot men nor gegebn di groyse, hobn mir gehat zeyer groyse tsvey shenk

00:17:35.526 --> 00:17:43.170
un hot mir hot gegebn di shenk, UNK eyns iz gevezn a zilber shank un eyne iz gevezn a sforim shank, dort hobn mir ir dos alts gegebn

00:17:43.170 --> 00:17:46.240
dem tish fun esn m'hot zikh der tate mitgenumen

00:17:46.240 --> 00:17:48.342
keyn S- UNK

00:17:48.342 --> 00:17:50.023
mitgenumen mit di benklekh

00:17:50.023 --> 00:17:54.303
shvartse lederne benklekh, gedenk ikh nokh vi haynt, dos iz gevezn.

00:17:54.303 --> 00:17:58.064
oyf dem tish un oyf di benklekh ho'mir undz geshlofn.

00:17:58.965 --> 00:18:00.123
vu

00:17:59.083 --> 00:18:01.912
di kinder, in, in PODGORZE.

00:18:02.104 --> 00:18:04.463
vayl mir ho'mir nisht gehat mer vi tsvey betn

00:18:04.463 --> 00:18:09.118
mit a shank un dem tish mit di benklekh, un oyf dem ze'mir undz geshlofn.

00:18:09.023 --> 00:18:12.105
un vos hot ir nokh gekent mitnemen fun

00:18:11.503 --> 00:18:15.530
di zakhn, nor bloyz di zakhn, gornisht epes andersh, nor di zakhn.

00:18:15.250 --> 00:18:19.429
un ver iz mit aykh geven in geto fun ayer familye?

00:18:18.253 --> 00:18:22.493
di gantse familye. undz ze'mir gevezn di gantse familye di gantse tsayt in geto

00:18:22.493 --> 00:18:24.653
UNK vos geyt di gantse may-

00:18:24.653 --> 00:18:29.490
mayne g- mayn mame m- mit di kinder ze- m- undz tsv- dray geshvister zenen mir dort gevezn.

00:18:29.490 --> 00:18:31.528
di bobe iz gevezn in Makev

00:18:32.530 --> 00:18:36.472
un di andere yunge mentshn zenen geganen

00:18:37.305 --> 00:18:43.166
zenen gan oykhet in geto arayn der bruder fun di mame iz gan in geto arayn. di shvester iz gegan in geto arayn

00:18:43.166 --> 00:18:45.382
zenen oykhet gegan in geto arayn

00:18:45.574 --> 00:18:50.659
un di, di bobe, eltere mentshn hot men shoyn moyre gehat vider tsu nemen in geto arayn UNK m'hot zey bald

00:18:50.659 --> 00:18:57.195
ersht hobn zey nisht gehat keyn arbet ⟨vos⟩ zenen gevezn eltere mentshn, hot me- zenen zey geforn keyn Makev ⟨vayl⟩ di bobe shtamt fun Makev.

00:18:57.690 --> 00:18:59.439
zenen geforn keyn Makev.

00:18:59.428 --> 00:19:00.957
un ayer foter?

00:19:01.015 --> 00:19:05.818
mayn foter iz gevezn mit undz tsuzamen di gantse tsayt, hot er oykhet gehat nebekh a bruder

00:19:05.892 --> 00:19:07.576
mit fir k- kinder

00:19:07.576 --> 00:19:09.803
un in geto hot men takesh tsugenumen

00:19:09.803 --> 00:19:11.100
dem bruder

00:19:11.781 --> 00:19:19.132
mit di froy, un di dray kinder zenen arayngekumen nokh in d- undzer WOHNUNG arayn. UNK hobn mir gehat tsvey shtubn gedungen in PODGORZE

00:19:19.155 --> 00:19:20.887
tsvey shtub mit a kokh.

00:19:21.045 --> 00:19:24.715
shpeter, yedes mol iz dos geto klener gevorn.

00:19:24.715 --> 00:19:29.035
iz gevezn, m'hot tsugenumen a shtik. m'hot gemakht oyszidlungen keyn MAJDANEK, keyn k-

00:19:29.035 --> 00:19:31.075
TREBLINKA, di mentshn tsugenumen

00:19:31.075 --> 00:19:33.791
un yedes mol iz di geto klener gevorn

00:19:33.791 --> 00:19:43.685
iz zenen, zenen gekumen di shvester fun di mame, hot gevoynt oyf ⟨EINE⟩ teyl, ⟨iz es⟩ gekumen ⟨tsu mir, ober⟩ yeder iz antlofn. m'hot gevust az do geyt men shoyn vider klener makhn.

00:19:43.708 --> 00:19:45.637
di, di kapos

00:19:45.637 --> 00:19:47.955
zey hobn gevust ⟨A PROPRE⟩

00:19:48.062 --> 00:19:50.972
ven vet zayn di oyszidlung, ven vet zayn di

00:19:50.972 --> 00:19:55.012
di, m'vet tsumakhn vider a shtik fun geto. zey hobn dos alts gevust.

00:19:55.012 --> 00:19:56.243
un demolts

00:19:56.243 --> 00:20:02.315
ven m'hot tsugemakht in geto yedes mol a shtikele, hobn zey nor gehat kinder un eltere mentshn.

00:20:02.322 --> 00:20:05.826
di mentshn vos zey hobn gekent arbetn hot men zey nokh gelozt

00:20:06.085 --> 00:20:08.762
azoy vi undz ze'mir gevezn kinder

00:20:08.852 --> 00:20:12.946
iz vider gevezn dos zelbe. der tate hot dokh nisht gevolt zoln mir undz zayn

00:20:13.223 --> 00:20:15.407
zey ⟨veln⟩ undz got bahit UNK tsunemen

00:20:15.407 --> 00:20:17.447
hot er undz aroysgeshikt tsu di goye

00:20:17.447 --> 00:20:20.017
⟨undzere⟩ meshores UNK. bald

00:20:20.040 --> 00:20:26.969
az di yekes zenen arayngekumen, hot men gezogt az s'megt nisht zayn keyn meshorsim bay di yidn. ale meshorsim zenen geganen avek

00:20:27.195 --> 00:20:29.588
iz zi avekgef- -ganen tsu a shvester

00:20:29.588 --> 00:20:33.039
ABER undz ze'mir zeyer gut gevezn mit di shvester un mir ir

00:20:33.039 --> 00:20:39.595
azoy az bin yedes mol gelofn tsu di goye, mitn TRAM, tsvishn TRAM antlofn, ikh mit mayn shvester

00:20:39.595 --> 00:20:41.300
zenen mir gelofn tsu di goye.

00:20:41.300 --> 00:20:44.976
ABER yednfal hobn mir zeyer moyre gehat tsu zayn bay di goye.

00:20:45.150 --> 00:20:47.844
undzer goye iz gevezn a gute.

00:20:48.340 --> 00:20:52.791
zi hot, nor vos ⟨zi⟩ hot gehat dem feler, zi hot getrunken, azoy vi ale polyakn.

00:20:52.791 --> 00:20:53.851
zey trinken.

00:20:54.043 --> 00:20:57.429
zi hot zikh gekoyft a ⟨pontshek⟩ un trinken, hobn mir dokh moyre gehat

00:20:57.469 --> 00:21:00.483
az zi vet dos oyszogn az zi hot di yidishe kinder

00:21:00.979 --> 00:21:09.186
ober iz gevezn geblibn, az nisht voltn mir ge- mit ir yo geblibn, vayl zi hot gevolt zoln mir dingen a WOHNUNG ergets in a dorf un un nemen tsu undz ale dray kinder tsuzamen.

00:21:09.186 --> 00:21:11.446
nemen ⟨tsu zey⟩ UNK zogn az dos iz ire kinder.

00:21:11.446 --> 00:21:15.816
ABER m'hot nisht gekent dos makhn, vayl zi iz gevezn a trinker, hot men moyre gehat.

00:21:15.816 --> 00:21:19.672
ABER oyf di eyne tsvey dray nekht zenen mir yo geganen tsu ir

00:21:19.672 --> 00:21:21.422
un m'hot zikh arayngeleygt

00:21:21.422 --> 00:21:24.412
a gantsn tog hobn mir gekent ⟨arum⟩geyn in di shtub.

00:21:24.412 --> 00:21:28.487
vayl di shvester iz avekgeganen oyf a mark s- mit kroyt, m- feser mit

00:21:28.487 --> 00:21:30.447
kroyt demolts hot men farkoyft

00:21:30.578 --> 00:21:34.127
iz zi avekgeganen oyf a mark, azoy az undz ho'mir zikh

00:21:34.127 --> 00:21:37.397
gedreyt in di shtub. shpeter bay nakht zenen zey tsurikgekumen

00:21:37.397 --> 00:21:39.477
zenen dokh gekumen farshidene mentshn

00:21:39.477 --> 00:21:42.147
hobn mir, hot zi undz tsugebet in di bet gevant

00:21:42.147 --> 00:21:43.347
in bet

00:21:43.347 --> 00:21:45.927
⟨in⟩ gantsn mit di bet gevant fun oybn

00:21:45.927 --> 00:21:47.951
undz ho'mir nisht gekent keyn otem khapn

00:21:47.951 --> 00:21:50.791
azoy hot zi undz tsugedekt biz zi iz gekumen shlofn.

00:21:50.791 --> 00:21:55.328
az zi iz gekumen shlofn, hot zi undz ar- avekgerukt dos bet gevant, zoln mir kenen otem khapn

00:21:55.485 --> 00:22:00.845
iz shpeter, zi iz geforn kukn yedes mol vi azoy halt zikh dor- undz ho'mir dokh nisht gevolt blaybn

00:22:00.845 --> 00:22:02.835
m'hot gevolt geyn tsu di eltern tsurik

00:22:03.062 --> 00:22:06.988
iz hot zi gezogt az s'iz shoyn fertik, zenen mir vider tsurik arayngelofn.

00:22:06.808 --> 00:22:11.024
un vi iz dos geven meglekh az ir zolt aroysgeyn fun geto? iz geven

00:22:11.024 --> 00:22:15.004
meglekhkeytn arayn un aroystsugeyn fray?

00:22:13.035 --> 00:22:18.837
s'iz nisht gevezn UNK. ikh hob in di minut fartseylt az s'iz gevezn a TRAM vos eyn TRAM ⟨iz⟩ geforn fun eyn zayt

