ir veyst ver zey zenen geven?

00:23:30.087 --> 00:23:33.537
ikh ken nisht zogn keyn nomen, vayl ikh veys nisht. ikh hob nisht i-

00:23:33.537 --> 00:23:36.587
demolts nisht farshtanen vos heyst a nomen demolts far zey

