vi hot er geheysn?

00:24:31.984 --> 00:24:40.095
iz UNK "tu op a hitl, un vets retn dayne kinder." zogt er "ikh vel nisht retn ma- mayne kinder. ikh vel nisht leygn a tsveytn in der erd arayn"

00:24:40.135 --> 00:24:42.915
hot er gezogt. "ikh muz dokh yenem oysgebn.

00:24:42.915 --> 00:24:45.925
ikh vel nisht oysgebn. durkh mayne kinder zol ikh yenem oysgebn

00:24:45.925 --> 00:24:48.313
dos zol ikh a kapo nisht ontun keyn hitl.

00:24:48.808 --> 00:24:52.885
az s'vet zayn bashert vet men azoy lebn, un az ⟨NO⟩ iz oykhet farfaln" hot er gezogt.

00:24:53.061 --> 00:24:55.080
hot nisht gevolt ontun keyn hitele.

00:24:56.470 --> 00:24:58.677
un m'hot dortn gehaltn

