shule gornisht.

00:25:21.647 --> 00:25:23.787
nisht gevezn iber hoypt keyn shules.

00:25:23.773 --> 00:25:24.627
UNK

00:25:23.787 --> 00:25:26.264
di gantse tsayt nisht gevezn keyn shules.

00:25:25.849 --> 00:25:28.745
un vos hobn di kinder gemakht azoy?

00:25:27.672 --> 00:25:30.096
gornisht. m'hot zikh gedreyt oyf di gasn.

00:25:30.253 --> 00:25:31.474
gornisht gemakht

00:25:31.474 --> 00:25:32.846
di gantse tsayt.

00:25:32.802 --> 00:25:36.677
