00:25:36.463 --> 00:25:43.021
yo, hot yo geklert ar- nisht azoy avektsuloyfn, nor mayn tate hot zikh gemakht arishe papirn

00:25:43.450 --> 00:25:49.757
un hot gemeynt az me vet kenen geyn oyf di arishe papirn, un ikh hob oykhet gehat, un mayn shvester oykhet, ale

00:25:49.757 --> 00:25:53.137
hot gekost a sakh gelt dos tun. dos hot men gemakht a galekh

