di mame hot gekent perfekt poylish.

00:26:10.151 --> 00:26:12.012
vet zikh makhn vi er iz a shtumer.

00:26:12.019 --> 00:26:15.962
⟨iz⟩ azoy gegan, ABER di mame hot zeyer moyre gehat. "vu zol ikh geyn?

